<h4> 20. Which is the best answer for (가)? [3점] </h4>

 <div class="bogi"><p>
    ① You should do the dishes. <br>
    ② I am so tired, so let's take a rest. <br>
    ③ The earth is dying because we spend too much water. <br>
    ④ You should bring paper cups and plates to save trees. <br>
    ⑤ We can save lots of trees by not using paper cups and plates. <br>
